
0.1 - 2016/01/01
  * Initial release of the module to CPAN.
  * Sending "all on" and "all off" events works.
  * Detecting and displaying details about light-bulbs works.

0.2 - 2016/01/01
  * Controlling a bulb individually works:
	* Turning on.
	* Turning off.
	* Setting brightness.
	* Setting RGBW values.
        * Setting the temperature.
